Package de.edux.augmentation.effects.geomentry

Enum-Klasse Perspective

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Perspective>
de.edux.augmentation.effects.geomentry.Perspective
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
Serializable, Comparable<Perspective>, Constable
public enum Perspective extends Enum<Perspective>
Defines common perspective transformations that can be applied to images. Each enum constant represents a predefined set of affine transformations that mimic the effect of changing the perspective from which an image is viewed.
